{"tid":1985101,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"如何處理假訊息？Youtube執行長：與WHO建議不同的內容都會刪除","createTime":"2020-04-23T02:20:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T06:12:52.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0fa90c974ee3366ae274b1e874ad9bb265ad4e2","tid":1985101,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"如何處理假訊息？Youtube執行長：與WHO建議不同的內容都會刪除<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-22/395310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-04-22%2F395310&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6myprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=042efa86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-04-22/395310</a><br />\n<br />\n2019新型冠狀病毒疾病（COVID-19，武漢肺炎）疫情持續延燒，相關不實訊息頻頻在社群平台上流竄，對此，Youtube執行長沃西基(Susan Wojcicki)在接受CNN節目訪問時表示，任何沒有醫學證實的訊息，或是與WHO建議不同的內容，都將會因為違反Youtube的平台政策遭到刪除。<br />\n<br />\n沃西基在接受CNN電視節目《Reliable Sources》訪問時表示，今年開始，平台上的具權威消息的新聞類影片點閱率，相比去年同期增加了75％，顯示民眾對這些資訊的需求。"},{"pid":"0dff8e0acb734d520945bba1e1d523fb17197460","tid":1985101,"uid":19552,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:21:46.000Z","msg":"其實都幾服YOUTUBE<br />\n比支那封鎖 又抄鳩你但會咁徹底奶共"},{"pid":"2d8554e33acb767241205247a78df2a5b6b0dbe7","tid":1985101,"uid":153600,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆本身喺美國都已經好黑人憎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家佢仲搞啲咁嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac5ac88fc768e92ab036f28821479174a0aa2ae5","tid":1985101,"uid":166360,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T02:24:08.000Z","msg":"咁叫人戴口罩的影片肯定遭殃"},{"pid":"a636ee0cf43496bd6be83604e78096fd189e3158","tid":1985101,"uid":79563,"like":0,